title: How to Make Gluten Free Tex Mex Breakfast Tacos

steps.headline: Grease the pan thoroughly with cooking spray.
Turn the stove burner to medium-high.
Crack the eggs into pan and beat.
Sprinkle the steamed rice with taco seasoning and mix well.
As the scrambled eggs begin to cook, add black beans, seasoned rice, and both cheeses.
Watch contents of pan carefully until eggs are cooked and cheese is melted.
Wrap the eggs and other ingredients in corn tortillas and serve!

text: Grease the pan thoroughly with cooking spray.  Turn the stove burner to medium-high.  Crack the eggs into pan and beat.  Sprinkle the steamed rice with taco seasoning and mix well.  As the scrambled eggs begin to cook, add black beans, seasoned rice, and both cheeses.  Stir thoroughly.  Watch contents of pan carefully until eggs are cooked and cheese is melted.  Turn the stove off.  Wrap the eggs and other ingredients in corn tortillas and serve!
